{"tid":1017029,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人要睇同一套電影幾次先可以完整睇完？","createTime":"2019-02-11T07:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T09:59:12.000Z","uid":171272,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6c0d81852cd76f23cf87c4203fc9cb68ab66a96a","tid":1017029,"uid":171272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S0QSawM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS0QSawM.png&h=2acd0487&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人類平均一日眨2萬次眼<br />\n每次大概0.3秒<br />\n除開大概4.02秒眨一次消耗0.3秒嘅眨眼<br />\n<br />\n如果一套電影100 分鐘，途中大概會眨1388.88...次眼<br />\n即係最少有416.66.. 秒你係無望到個mon<br />\n佔全套電影嘅6.94%時間<br />\n<br />\n假設呢個計算合理，大概幾次先可以完整睇完一套電影？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誤差：<br />\n1）每人每日每次眨眼嘅次數時間都唔同<br />\n2）排除電影會有過於刺眼或令人下意識合埋眼嘅場景（例如：驚嚇、噁心、催淚等等場景）<br />\n3）無視左「人係睇電子產品、影音嘅時候眨眼次數會較少」呢個事實<br />\n4）假設睇電影嘅人雙眼係正常狀態"},{"pid":"9281627e79a60e0fa64d10e6b766ce7d2d08c285","tid":1017029,"uid":176802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0d430809bbdcee18c773a0602a6991d35ac806","tid":1017029,"uid":511,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2gwU8pZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2gwU8pZ.png&h=074117d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"546ac7f5e6231a70bfc2c08f53b34a5106173510","tid":1017029,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"遲早有人工視覺<br />\n用隻假眼睇野 自動傳入大腦 產生影像<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}